modShortDescription: For when you need to build underwater without drowning, this crafted diving mask keeps you oxygenated and somewhat warm under the surface.
modDescription:
For when you need to build underwater without drowning, this crafted diving mask keeps you oxygenated and somewhat warm under the surface.

Tiny server-side modlet. The [mask](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-clothing/) does not require any perks, books or workbench to craft. It looks like a hazmat mask when worn. Very dashing.

**[Download](https://github.com/CupOfTeal/UnderWaterBreathingDivingMask/archive/refs/heads/main.zip)**

**Credits:** [Khym](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/khym/)
